{"tid":2238243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"又1國！巴基斯坦正式封殺TikTok","createTime":"2020-10-11T03:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T10:23:06.000Z","uid":141151,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d61c5a97215c916990f8b0f6b6d91c858aed55de","tid":2238243,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"又1國！巴基斯坦正式封殺TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3317038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3317038&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=b11a2710\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3317038&h=0c343688\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3317038</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕早前有消息指出，巴基斯坦將封殺中國短影音平台TikTok。巴基斯坦電信監管機構週五正式宣佈禁TikTok，因為該App無法過濾「不道德及不雅的內容」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，巴基斯坦電信管理局（PTA）週五表示，這項禁令是基於「社會不同階層對該平台不道德及不雅內容的投訴」。PTA指出，在TikTok減少非法內容後，他們將重新審查禁令。<br />\n<br />\nTikTok則表示一直與PTA保持定期溝通及合作，希望能就此事得出結論，並繼續為巴基斯坦提供服務。<br />\n<br />\n據分析公司Sensor Tower數據，TikTok在巴基斯坦每月將近有2000萬名活躍用戶，在過去12個月中，TikTok在巴基斯坦是繼WhatsApp及臉書之後下載量排行第3的應用程式。"},{"pid":"14a376a85a67a9bfedab17981446e72b81f9620b","tid":2238243,"uid":144001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T03:48:23.000Z","msg":"巴中有好呢 又掉轉槍頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694ee66a83785cd1fee1cf06cf94f89a73eea1b8","tid":2238243,"uid":371849,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"唔係話巴鐵咩"},{"pid":"0314ab86d9b5f0060936d465701d96f44fc71782","tid":2238243,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"tiktok 有咩不